Gathering EXP is a key resource in the game, playing a vital role in boosting resource collection efficiency and character capabilities. Players accumulate experience through activities such as logging and mining to increase gathering skill levels. Skill levels determine collection speed, rare resource acquisition probability, and unlocking of higher-level skills. As the game progresses, character needs become more complex, making high gathering skills essential for support.
